<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Do you want to understand the world of antiquity in all of its colorful complexity? In the Classical Civilization minor, you can immerse yourself in Greek &amp; Roman mythology, history, poetry, archaeology, philosophy, art, politics, religion, and drama, all while building skills that will equip you for a wide range of careers.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
